column1: # This file is a tab-delimited table of read counts and accession numbers
# for the samples from the winter 2018 S&R experiments with the 68 strain
# raw_n_pairs           number of read pairs in the raw data
# trimmed_n_pairs       number of read pairs left after quality trimming
# aln_n_reads           number of reads (not pairs!) that aligned to USDA1106 (reference)
# marked_dups           number of reads marked as PCR duplicates by samtools
# dup_rate              proportion of reads that were marked as duplicates
# aln_rate              proportion of trimmed reads that aligned to the reference
# sra_accession         SRA accession for this pool
# description           Brief description of host genotype, community, and other conditions
